   abstract={The composition dependence of the lattice parameter (αβ) for the bcc (β) phase in the Zr-Nb system at room temperature has been established by combining new experiments with an assessment of previously published data on bcc Nb, bcc Zr and their alloys The experimental part of the work comprises neutron scattering measurements on alloys with Nb contents between 13 and 48 at% Nb, quenched from high temperatures A detailed comparison is performed with previous X-ray measurements The present results are also used in testing the applicability of Vegard's law in the Zr-Nb system, and in determining the probable αβ value for Zr, which cannot be measured at room temperature (orig)},
